    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a fantastic car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the oil changes and care, so it runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
