    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a sharp, linear power band. The drivetrain features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry remains precise, providing the communicative feedback and lateral grip expected of this chassis. This is a driver-focused example with a healthy powertrain and sorted vitals, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
