    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive overall shape. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is clean and intact, and every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is a dream. It has been serviced regularly, ensuring a smooth, responsive drive with a solid suspension and firm braking. You are getting a dependable, stylish ride that looks and feels much younger than its mileage suggests. Perfect for anyone seeking a turn-key vehicle that balances quality with value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
