    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in great shape for its next owner. It drives like a dream and has been really well-loved\u2014perfect if you're looking for something dependable and ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
