      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, facilitated by eight individual throttle bodies and a sophisticated VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis remains taut with excellent lateral rigidity; the M Variable Differential Lock provides optimal traction through the rear wheels. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator refurbishment, addressing common S65 pain points. The suspension retains its factory damping characteristics, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the communicative feedback sought by purists. Finished in a classic palette, this example shows honest wear consistent with a driver\u2019s car that has been maintained to a high mechanical standard.",
